945882-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::2491cb00-1384-11ef-821d-f1a8c6d3224a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Professional Background:\n\nCaptain Šime has over 20 years of experience in yachting. He will provide you with an incredible cruising experience and reveal the most beautiful parts of the Croatian coast. Due to his extensive experience, you will feel secure in all weather conditions. Indulge yourself and enjoy your vacation in the hands of a top professional.\n\nPersonal Interests:\n\nIn his free time, Captain Šime loves spending time in the vineyard and dedicating himself to wine, which you can taste on the yacht Karizma.\n\nLanguages Spoken:\n\nEnglish, Croatian\n\nTestimonial:\n\n»Captain Šime left a special impression on us with his charisma and took us to the most beautiful places we could imagine. For the first time, we truly felt what it means to be in paradise.« - satisfied guests"},{"name":"Marko Stančić","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::77945882-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::a0450e20-b0a4-11ef-ae41-4fc2702df187/{imageVariant}","role":"Chef","bio":"Our chef, Marko, is a humble soul in the turmoil of culinary minds, an expert in hospitality. From the very start, thrown into the fire of cuisine through Italy, Switzerland, and across oceanic vessels. Completely dedicated to each ingredient, extracting the finest aromas for your palate. Be assured that the dishes you taste are prepared with utmost love, and with every bite, you'll crave more.\n\nPersonal Interests:\n\nMarko loves his work and that it's the only way to endure the heat, early mornings, stress, and responsibility. But when the workday ends, he's a true hedonist. He enjoys peace, fishing, and spending time with his family and his faithful friends.\n\nLanguages Spoken:\n\nEnglish, Serbian, Croatian, Macedonian, Bulgarian\n\nSignature Dishes:\n\nSlow-roasted lamb and veal, Risotto with cuttlefish ink, and Pasta \"Pomodoro Fresco\" with homemade tomatoes and onions. You will be surprised how modern traditional dishes can look."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":7000000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":7000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":8000000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":8000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"SEASON A (From 18 April 2026 till 16 May 2026) & SEASON E (From 19 September 2026 till 31 October 2026)","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-04-18T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-16T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-19T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-10-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":7000000,"inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":7000000,"amount":7000000,"conditions":"Weekly"}],"total":7000000,"subTotal":7000000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Croatia","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Croatia"],"coordinates":[16.818610292079534,44.700266827856225],"bbox":[13.517187500000006,42.432910156249996,19.400976562500006,46.534619140625]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"SEASON B (From 16 May 2026 till 13 June 2026) & SEASON D (From 29 August 2026 till 19 September 2026)","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-05-16T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-06-13T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-08-29T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-09-19T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":7500000,"inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":7500000,"amount":7500000,"conditions":"Weekly"}],"total":7500000,"subTotal":7500000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Croatia","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Croatia"],"coordinates":[16.818610292079534,44.700266827856225],"bbox":[13.517187500000006,42.432910156249996,19.400976562500006,46.534619140625]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"SEASON C (F